schedule.appointment.timeSlot

Class Timeslot

  • java.lang.Object
    • schedule.appointment.timeSlot.Timeslot
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<Timeslot>

    public class Timeslot
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<Timeslot>
    The Timeslot class creates valid timeslots for vaccination appointments. Uses both the date and time class to create the timeslot and enables these timeslots to be compared to one another in both date and time.
    Author:
    Jah C. Speed, Abe Vitangcol
